<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">stele</rs>, slightly damaged (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">1.42</measure>, <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.525</measure>, <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.20</measure>). There is a pediment above, outlined with moulding and flanked by small <rs type="decoration">acroteria</rs>. For a full description see Smith, l.c.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the lower part of the face, <measure type="length" unit="metre">0.54</measure> below the pediment (so presumably below a painted image). The layout is compressed and irregular.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Second-early 1st century B.C.; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.01-0.015</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
